&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are so crazy about apps right now you wouldn't believe it. If you have recommendations, tips, or just want to let us know about your own app, drop a note in the comments or &lt;a href="mailto:cchan@gizmodo.com"&gt;shoot me an email.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;
